data.description: ***ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT 3.88%***  ***Seller willing to offer 3k in concessions!***  Welcome to your dream home at 14736 Hooded Merganser in the desirable Redbird Ranch neighborhood of San Antonio, TX. This captivating single-family home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, making it the perfect oasis for you and your family. Located conveniently close to Lackland AFB.    Upon entering, you'll be immediately drawn to the open floor plan and stunning kitchen. The spacious layout provides ample room for entertaining guests or relaxing with loved ones. Imagine preparing your favorite meals in this well-appointed kitchen, complete with modern appliances and plenty of counter space for all your culinary creations. One of the standout features of this property is the Texas sized backyard, offering endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment and recreational activities. Picture yourself hosting barbecues, playing catch with the kids, or simply unwinding in your own private sanctuary. Additionally, all the bedrooms are conveniently located upstairs, creating a cozy and comfortable environment for rest and relaxation. Priced at $270,000, this remarkable property presents an incredible opportunity to own a slice of paradise in one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in San Antonio. Whether you're a first-time buyer or looking to upgrade, this home offers tremendous value and a lifestyle like no other.
